    "shortDescription": "<p>This spell functions like @Compendium[pf1.spells.cfzk3vkv1c7ncaug]{Magic Fang}, except that the enhancement bonus on attack and damage rolls is +1 per four caster levels (maximum +5). This bonus does not allow a natural weapon or unarmed strike to bypass damage reduction aside from magic.</p>\n<p>Alternatively, you may imbue all of the creature's natural weapons with a +1 enhancement bonus (regardless of your caster level).</p>\n<p>Greater <em>magic fang</em> can be made permanent with a @Compendium[pf1.spells.nsxngq65mbrzgwnm]{Permanency} spell.</p>"
